  "detailed_description": "Explorer Daniel finally obtains the map of the hidden treasure after a long quest. He parachutes onto the location of the treasure, a place not visible on the world map. Our hero must navigate through a challenging and perilous journey, overcoming deadly traps, to ultimately reach the great treasure.<br><br>Will you be able to reach the treasure despite all the obstacles and traps, or will you become a Bondman of Traps?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/8c34fb2713cfe7fe518c761115b02639.poster.avif?t=1771107749\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/8c34fb2713cfe7fe518c761115b02639.webm?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/8c34fb2713cfe7fe518c761115b02639.mp4?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquer the Challenging Platforms One by One</h2><br>Passing through platform elements is truly challenging. In some platform sections, you must make quick decisions and take action. So, plan, prepare, and take action. There's no need to rush. Or is there?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/43e4e9047c83bb1cfc1e3d7be4a2c865.poster.avif?t=1771107749\" width=598 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/43e4e9047c83bb1cfc1e3d7be4a2c865.webm?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/43e4e9047c83bb1cfc1e3d7be4a2c865.mp4?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game features different mechanics filled with surprises in some platform elements. You can't rely only on traps; platforms may also deceive you and contain traps for you to make mistakes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Identify and Solve the Traps</h2><br>Most traps will take your life and try to kill you. Recognize the obstacles, analyze the movements, and improve your reflexes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/d5be347528a49d38af2e52b27a09f946.poster.avif?t=1771107749\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/d5be347528a49d38af2e52b27a09f946.webm?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/d5be347528a49d38af2e52b27a09f946.mp4?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trust Yourself and Your Reflexes</h2><br>In Bondman Of Traps, dozens of traps and numerous platform elements will do their best to make you fail in this journey. So, what will you do? Accept this challenge. Solve the secrets of the traps. Improve your reflexes and show them who you are.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/f82481314b79105be77429adc92c2475.poster.avif?t=1771107749\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/f82481314b79105be77429adc92c2475.webm?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/f82481314b79105be77429adc92c2475.mp4?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Explorer Daniel finally obtains the map of the hidden treasure after a long quest. He parachutes onto the location of the treasure, a place not visible on the world map. Our hero must navigate through a challenging and perilous journey, overcoming deadly traps, to ultimately reach the great treasure.<br><br>Will you be able to reach the treasure despite all the obstacles and traps, or will you become a Bondman of Traps?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/8c34fb2713cfe7fe518c761115b02639.poster.avif?t=1771107749\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/8c34fb2713cfe7fe518c761115b02639.webm?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/8c34fb2713cfe7fe518c761115b02639.mp4?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquer the Challenging Platforms One by One</h2><br>Passing through platform elements is truly challenging. In some platform sections, you must make quick decisions and take action. So, plan, prepare, and take action. There's no need to rush. Or is there?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/43e4e9047c83bb1cfc1e3d7be4a2c865.poster.avif?t=1771107749\" width=598 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/43e4e9047c83bb1cfc1e3d7be4a2c865.webm?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/43e4e9047c83bb1cfc1e3d7be4a2c865.mp4?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game features different mechanics filled with surprises in some platform elements. You can't rely only on traps; platforms may also deceive you and contain traps for you to make mistakes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Identify and Solve the Traps</h2><br>Most traps will take your life and try to kill you. Recognize the obstacles, analyze the movements, and improve your reflexes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/d5be347528a49d38af2e52b27a09f946.poster.avif?t=1771107749\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/d5be347528a49d38af2e52b27a09f946.webm?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/d5be347528a49d38af2e52b27a09f946.mp4?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trust Yourself and Your Reflexes</h2><br>In Bondman Of Traps, dozens of traps and numerous platform elements will do their best to make you fail in this journey. So, what will you do? Accept this challenge. Solve the secrets of the traps. Improve your reflexes and show them who you are.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/f82481314b79105be77429adc92c2475.poster.avif?t=1771107749\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/f82481314b79105be77429adc92c2475.webm?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703290/extras/f82481314b79105be77429adc92c2475.mp4?t=1771107749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
